[SN]TITLE[SN]
Member of Aberdeen International Airport ground staff injured

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A member of ground staff at Aberdeen International Airport has been taken to hospital after suffering leg injuries in an accident.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident, at about 07:30, happened 'airside' but not on the runway and involved the man's own vehicle.
An airport spokesman said there was no impact on operations, and an investigation would be carried out.
